Package org.apache.wayang.core.function

Class ReduceDescriptor<Type>

java.lang.Object
org.apache.wayang.core.function.FunctionDescriptor
org.apache.wayang.core.function.ReduceDescriptor<Type>
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
WrappedReduceDescriptor
public class ReduceDescriptor<Type> extends FunctionDescriptor
This descriptor pertains to functions that take multiple data units and aggregate them into a single data unit by means of a tree-like fold, i.e., using a commutative, associative function..
